These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
House: wooden, art-deco, victorian, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
4. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the townhouse house is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| House   | townhouse | wooden     | victorian | art-deco |
| Beverage     | almond-milk     | hot-chocolate | mirinda  | juice      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, chess, reading, fishing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, dahlia, lily
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Hobby   | dancing | chess    | fishing     | reading  |
| Flower     | zinnia    | dahlia | azalea | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, writing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | go   | bridge  | chess |
| Hobby           | puzzles | woodworking | writing | skydiving  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, dubstep, house
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, light-blue, red, emerald
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of house is between the fan of indie and the person who likes red##2
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of blues##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | blues | indie | house | dubstep  |
| Color   | light-blue  | apricot   | emerald  | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, october, september
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, animation, sports, scientific
1. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Birthday   | november    | february   | october | september    |
| Movie-Genre      | animation | musical | sports       | scientific |

