.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, western, action, superhero
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, futuristic, colonial
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the futuristic house is between the colonial house and the person watching action movies##2
3. the gothic-revival house is between the futuristic house and the person watching family movies##2
4. the colonial house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre    | family | action | superhero | western |
| House   | townhouse | gothic-revival  | futuristic    | colonial  |

