.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, mouse, rat
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, zucchini, onion, mango
1. the person eating mango is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the rat##2
5. the person eating zucchini is the person eating zucchini##1
6. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating onion and the owner of the rat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | dog | rat | mouse | rabbit     |
| Food     | pineapple | mango  | zucchini   | onion |

