.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, avocado, eggplant, cucumber
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, may, march
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food         | cucumber | eggplant | watermelon | avocado   |
| Birthday   | december | may | february      | march |

