2. the spanish is on the far right##1
3. the spanish is the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growstulip is between the japanese and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower     | iris | tulip   | sunflower      | lily      |
| Nationality   | japanese     | russian | turkish | spanish |

