.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, bird, hedgehog
4 different games are played: domino, go, canasta, scrabble
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing go##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Pet   | fish | guinea-pig | bird      | hedgehog   |
| Game   | canasta  | go    | domino | scrabble |

