.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, grey, white
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, april, july
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | light-blue | grey | white    | fuchsia      |
| Birthday   | april       | july       | december | june |

