.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, orange, artichoke, cauliflower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Food   | pineapple     | orange  | cauliflower | artichoke |
| Beverage     | tea | hot-chocolate | water     | almond-milk    |

