.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, thriller, sports, martial-arts
4 different games are played: whist, chess, go, billiard
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
4. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports  | martial-arts | thriller |
| Game           | go     | billiard | whist    | chess     |

