.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, tram, motorbike
City: berlin, paris, new-york, venice
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport   | airplane  | snowmobile | motorbike  | tram      |
| City    | venice | berlin | new-york | paris |

