.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, baseball, rugby
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game, dannemann, tiparillo
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
6. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby | baseball | climbing |
| Cigar   | tiparillo     | bolivar       | game   | dannemann      |

