.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, january, october
City: san-francisco, nizza, hamburg, miami
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | april | october | january | june |
| City         | nizza  | hamburg   | miami | san-francisco     |

