There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, coral, chestnut, mauve
1. the chinese is on the right of the british##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the british##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Nationality      | pakistani | brazilian    | british  | chinese |
| Color   | lavender       | coral | chestnut | mauve  |

