House: craftsman, modern, tower, cottage
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes ebony is the cottage house##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
5. the tower house is between the person who likes black and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Color   | yellow | ebony  | lilac  | black |
| House           | craftsman    | cottage | tower | modern |

