.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, march, december
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, broccoli, lettuce, papaya
1. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
2. the person eating papaya is the person eating papaya##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Birthday   | august     | june     | march          | december |
| Food      | pomegranate | broccoli | papaya | lettuce  |

 